    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that the more people try to \"help,\" the more it feels like they're just trying to keep me tethered to something that hurts. like they're forcing me to keep enduring this when there's no light at the end of it. i look at people who are healthy and it just seems so unfair that i have to stay in this loop of pain forever. it feels less like \"living\" and more like just... being punished.",
